         <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400\" data-kid=\"187\">Name / ID</div>\n                <div class=\"font-bold text-sm leading-tight\" data-kid=\"188\">Савельева Надежда Валерьевна</div>\n              </div>\n              <div data-kid=\"189\">\n                <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400\" data-kid=\"190\">Position</div>\n                <div class=\"font-bold text-xs text-[#0066B3]\" data-kid=\"191\">Директор УМЦ</div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"pt-4 border-t border-gray-100\" data-kid=\"192\">\n                <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-1\" data-kid=\"193\">Secure Email</div>\n                <a href=\"mailto:n.saveleva@narfu.ru\" class=\"text-xs hover:underline font-mono\" data-kid=\"194\">n.saveleva@narfu.ru</a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-200 relative group overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"195\">\n          <div class=\"barcode-decor\" data-kid=\"196\"></div>\n          <div class=\"p-8\" data-kid=\"197\">\n            <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-[#0066B3] mb-6 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading text-2xl\" data-kid=\"198\">ЛЛ</div>\n            <div class=\"space-y-4\" data-kid=\"199\">\n              <div data-kid=\"200\">\n                <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400\" data-kid=\"201\">Name / ID</div>\n                <div class=\"font-bold text-sm leading-tight\" data-kid=\"202\">Лещук Лаурита Васильевна</div>\n              </div>\n              <div data-kid=\"203\">\n                <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400\" data-kid=\"204\">Position</div>\n                <div class=\"font-bold text-xs text-[#0066B3]\" data-kid=\"205\">Менеджер проектов</div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"pt-4 border-t border-gray-100\" data-kid=\"206\">\n                <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-1\" data-kid=\"207\">Secure Email</div>\n                <a href=\"mailto:l.leshuk@narfu.ru\" class=\"text-xs hover:underline font-mono\" data-kid=\"208\">l.leshuk@narfu.ru</a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-200 relative group overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"209\">\n          <div class=\"barcode-decor\" data-kid=\"210\"></div>\n          <div class=\"p-8\" data-kid=\"211\">\n            <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-[#0066B3] mb-6 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading text-2xl\" data-kid=\"212\">КЮ</div>\n            <div class=\"space-y-4\" data-kid=\"213\">\n              <div data-kid=\"214\">\n                <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400\" data-kid=\"215\">Name / ID</div>\n                <div class=\"font-bold text-sm leading-tight\" data-kid=\"216\">Кузнецова Юлия Сергеевна</div>\n              </div>\n              <div data-kid=\"217\">\n                <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400\" data-kid=\"218\">Position</div>\n                <div class=\"font-bold text-xs text-[#0066B3]\" data-kid=\"219\">Менеджер проектов</div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"pt-4 border-t border-gray-100\" data-kid=\"220\">\n                <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-1\" data-kid=\"221\">Secure Email</div>\n                <a href=\"mailto:y.kuznetsova@narfu.ru\" class=\"text-xs hover:underline font-mono\" data-kid=\"222\">y.kuznetsova@narfu.ru</a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-200 relative group overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"223\">\n          <div class=\"barcode-decor\" data-kid=\"224\"></div>\n          <div class=\"p-8\" data-kid=\"225\">\n            <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-[#0066B3] mb-6 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading text-2xl\" data-kid=\"226\">КА</div>\n            <div class=\"space-y-4\" data-kid=\"227\">\n              <div data-kid=\"228\">\n                <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400\" data-kid=\"229\">Name / ID</div>\n                <div class=\"font-bold text-sm leading-tight\" data-kid=\"230\">Кононова Анастасия Александровна</div>\n              </div>\n              <div data-kid=\"231\">\n                <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400\" data-kid=\"232\">Position</div>\n                <div class=\"font-bold text-xs text-[#0066B3]\" data-kid=\"233\">Медиаменеджер</div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"pt-4 border-t border-gray-100\" data-kid=\"234\">\n                <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-1\" data-kid=\"235\">Secure Email</div>\n                <a href=\"mailto:a.kononova@narfu.ru\" class=\"text-xs hover:underline font-mono\" data-kid=\"236\">a.kononova@narfu.ru</a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"py-24 bg-white border-t border-gray-200\" data-kid=\"237\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8\" data-kid=\"238\">\n      <div class=\"mb-16\" data-kid=\"239\">\n        <h2 class=\"font-heading text-4xl mb-4 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"240\">Законодательная база РФ</h2>\n        <div class=\"text-xs font-mono-ui text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"241\">Legal responsibility & compliance</div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-12\" data-kid=\"242\">\n        <div class=\"border-l-4 border-[#0066B3] pl-8\" data-kid=\"243\">\n          <span class=\"font-heading text-xl text-[#0066B3] uppercase tracking-wide\" data-kid=\"244\">ТЕРРОРИЗМ</span>\n          <span class=\"text-gray-300 mx-2 font-mono-ui\" data-kid=\"245\">/</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"246\">Penal Code 205, 206, 281-281.3</span>\n          <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium\" data-kid=\"247\">\n            Полная уголовная ответственность за подготовку, осуществление или содействие террористической деятельности, а также диверсии на объектах инфраструктуры.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"border-l-4 border-[#0066B3] pl-8\" data-kid=\"248\">\n          <span class=\"font-heading text-xl text-[#0066B3] uppercase tracking-wide\" data-kid=\"249\">ЭКСТРЕМИЗМ</span>\n          <span class=\"text-gray-300 mx-2 font-mono-ui\" data-kid=\"250\">/</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"251\">Penal Code 282-282.3</span>\n          <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium\" data-kid=\"252\">\n            Ответственность за возбуждение ненависти либо вражды, а равно унижение человеческого достоинства по признакам пола, расы, национальности, языка.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"border-l-4 border-[#0066B3] pl-8\" data-kid=\"253\">\n          <span class=\"font-heading text-xl text-[#0066B3] uppercase tracking-wide\" data-kid=\"254\">ЛОЖНЫЕ СООБЩЕНИЯ</span>\n          <span class=\"text-gray-300 mx-2 font-mono-ui\" data-kid=\"255\">/</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"256\">Penal Code 207</span>\n          <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium\" data-kid=\"257\">\n            Уголовное наказание за заведомо ложное сообщение о готовящихся взрыве, поджоге или иных действиях, создающих опасность гибели людей.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"border-l-4 border-[#0066B3] pl-8\" data-kid=\"258\">\n          <span class=\"font-heading text-xl text-[#0066B3] uppercase tracking-wide\" data-kid=\"259\">ПУБЛИКАЦИИ</span>\n          <span class=\"text-gray-300 mx-2 font-mono-ui\" data-kid=\"260\">/</span>\n          <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"261\">Penal Code 167, 213</span>\n          <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium\" data-kid=\"262\">\n            Ответственность за хулиганство и умышленное уничтожение или повреждение имущества, включая распространение деструктивного контента.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <footer class=\"bg-[#002140] text-white py-20\" data-kid=\"263\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8\" data-kid=\"264\">\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between gap-16 mb-16\" data-kid=\"265\">\n        <div class=\"lg:w-1/3\" data-kid=\"266\">\n          <img src=\"/api/local/images/logo.png\" alt=\"САФУ\" class=\"h-12 mb-8\" data-kid=\"267\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-heading text-lg mb-6 leading-snug\" data-kid=\"268\">Северный (Арктический) федеральный университет имени М.В. Ломоносова</h4>\n          <p class=\"text-blue-200/60 text-sm leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"269\">\n            Координационный центр по противодействию идеологии терроризма и профилактике экстремизма в молодежной среде.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:w-1/2\" data-kid=\"270\">\n          <div data-kid=\"271\">\n            <div class=\"text-xs font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-[#0066B3] mb-6\" data-kid=\"272\">HQ Address</div>\n            <p class=\"text-sm mb-4\" data-kid=\"273\">г. Архангельск, ул. Ломоносова, 58</p>\n            <div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\" data-kid=\"274\">\n              <p data-kid=\"275\"><span class=\"opacity-50\" data-kid=\"276\">Admin:</span> +7 (8182) 65-05-22</p>\n              <p data-kid=\"277\"><span class=\"opacity-50\" data-kid=\"278\">Security:</span> +7 (8182) 21-85-01</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div data-kid=\"279\">\n            <div class=\"text-xs font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-[#0066B3] mb-6\" data-kid=\"280\">Digital Channels</div>\n            <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4\" data-kid=\"281\">\n              <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-[#0066B3] transition-colors flex items-center justify-center rounded-none border border-white/10\" data-kid=\"282\">\n                <i class=\"ti ti-brand-vk text-lg\" data-kid=\"283\"></i>\n              </a>\n              <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-[#0066B3] transition-colors flex items-center justify-center rounded-none border border-white/10\" data-kid=\"284\">\n                <i class=\"ti ti-world text-lg\" data-kid=\"285\"></i>\n              </a>\n              <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-[#0066B3] transition-colors flex items-center justify-center rounded-none border border-white/10\" data-kid=\"286\">\n                <i class=\"ti ti-mail text-lg\" data-kid=\"287\"></i>\n              </a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"pt-8 border-t border-white/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6\" data-kid=\"288\">\n        <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono-ui text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\" data-kid=\"289\">\n          © 2024 NArFU Coordination Center // All Rights Reserved\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-8 text-[10px] font-mono-ui uppercase tracking-widest text-white/50\" data-kid=\"290\">\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"291\">Security Policy</a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"292\">Vulnerability Disclosure</a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"293\">Institutional Auth</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</div>",
